- It's really good.

2617
01:23:49,484 --> 01:23:50,713
It has the scent of pine trees.

2618
01:23:50,714 --> 01:23:52,490
- It's fragrant.
- Because it's pine mushroom.

2619
01:23:52,514 --> 01:23:54,823
- My goodness.
- We need to brace ourselves.

2620
