- My gosh.

2683
01:26:01,984 --> 01:26:03,984
- Okay.
- What just happened?

2684
01:26:04,354 --> 01:26:05,584
What just happened?

2685
01:26:07,324 --> 01:26:08,753
- This is our fault.
- It is.

2686
01:26:08,754 --> 01:26:10,493
Our expectations were too high. Don't expect anything.

2687
01:26:10,494 --> 01:26:11,653
- Don't expect anything.
- Okay.

2688
